# The runner image only needs package.json and entrypoint.sh (see Dockerfile).
# Everything else in tests/e2e/ — specs, helpers, and especially the multi-MB
# videos/ and screenshots/ test output — would otherwise be uploaded to the
# Docker daemon as build context on every `docker build`. Whitelist only what
# the Dockerfile COPYs.
*
!package.json
!entrypoint.sh
